Package de.tud.kom.p2psim.overlay.bt

Interface Summary
BTDocument.BTBlockFinishedListener With this interface, other classes can be notified, if the download of a block finishes.
BTDocument.BTDocumentFinishedListener With this interface, other classes can be notified, if the download finishes.
BTDocument.BTPieceFinishedListener With this interface, other classes can be notified, if the download of a piece finishes.
 

Class Summary
BTBitSetUtil This class contains some usefull method if you have to work with bitfields.
BTClientApplication This class represents the client application and is the top most class of the client.
BTConnection This class stores the knowledge about the connection between two peers.
BTConstants This class encapsulates all constants of this BitTorrent implementation.
BTContact The basic knowledge of one peer about another peer: Its address and overlay id.
BTDataStore This class can be used for storing all kinds of data.
BTDebugUtils Some simple utils for debugging: If you use this methods, after you have finished, you can easiely find all uses of this methods(with eclipse) and delete them fast.
BTDocument This class represents the file, that the peers try to download.
BTFactory  
BTInternRequest This class is the peer intern representation of a request.
BTInternStatistic This class stores the statistic data in the clients.
BTMessageHandler This class handles most types of messages a peer can receive from other peers.
BTPeerDistributeNode This class is responsible for the communication with other peers.
BTPeerSearchNode This class is responsible for the communication with the tracker.
BTTorrent This class represents a '.torrent' file.
BTTrackerApplication This class represents the tracker application.
BTTrackerNode This class handles the trackers issues with the peers.
BTUtil This class defines some small helper methods.
